                <p>Shiny Pokemon are on the way to Pokemon Trading Card Game Pocket, and fans of these ultra-rare pocket monsters can expect to see them later this month. These sought-after Pokemon can be found through the new Shining Revelry booster packs that'll be available starting March 27, and The Pokemon Company is teasing shiny versions of Charizard ex, Lucario ex, and Pachirisu.</p><div tabindex="0" data-id="1703091530" data-promo-id="0" data-user-has-ads="1" data-video="{&quot;id&quot;:6465802,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Pok%C3%A9mon%20TCG%20Pocket%3A%20Shining%20Revelry%20%7C%20Official%20Trailer&quot;,&quot;lengthSeconds&quot;:43,&quot;startTime&quot;:0,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;share&quot;:{&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/pokemon-tcg-pocket-shining-revelry-official-trailer\/2300-6465802\/&quot;,&quot;embedUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465802\/&quot;,&quot;embedHtml&quot;:{&quot;640&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465802\/\&quot; height=\&quot;360\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;,&quot;480&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465802\/\&quot; height=\&quot;270\&quot; width=\&quot;480\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;}},&quot;device&quot;:&quot;other&quot;,&quot;isDevice&quot;:false,&quot;isLiveStream&quot;:false,&quot;videoType&quot;:&quot;video-on-demand&quot;,&quot;countdownTime&quot;:0,&quot;guid&quot;:&quot;gs-2300-6465802&quot;,&quot;ageGateCookieName&quot;:&quot;videoAgeGateBirthday&quot;,&quot;watchedCookieName&quot;:&quot;watchedVideoIds&quot;,&quot;watchedCookieDays&quot;:1,&quot;postPlayMax&quot;:100,&quot;uvpc&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;partne